The EnviBayes section operates under ISBA governance. Formal bylaws for the section are linked from the ISBA Environmental Sciences (EnviBayes) section page (see BYLAWS on that page).
In general, ISBA sections:

align officer roles and elections with the ISBA constitution and bylaws;
set section membership dues subject to ISBA Board approval;
report section activities to ISBA as required.

If anything on this site disagrees with the published ISBA materials, the ISBA website is authoritative.
